# Reflection

This exercise helped me understand the importance of approval workflows, branching logic, and governance in Salesforce automation.

### Key Learnings

* Approval workflows automate business decision-making.
* Branching logic allows flows to adapt dynamically to different scenarios.
* Governance ensures consistency, quality, and maintainability.
